---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Code of Conduct - Nepal Tek Community">
  <section class="py-24 bg-white min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6 uppercase tracking-tighter">
          Code of <span class="text-blue-600">Conduct</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed font-light">
          The Nepal Tech Community is committed to creating a safe and welcoming environment for everyone. This code outlines our expectations for behavior for all members, executives, sub-community captains, and event participants.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-12 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        <div class="p-8 bg-gray-50 rounded-[2rem] border border-gray-100">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Scope & Applicability</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            This Code of Conduct applies to <span class="font-bold text-blue-600">all individuals</span> involved with the Nepal Tech Community, including:
          </p>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-600"></div> Executive Team Members</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-600"></div> Sub-community Captains</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-600"></div> General Members</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-600"></div> Event Participants & Guests</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-[2rem]">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Be Respectful</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            We expect everyone to treat each other with respect. This includes respecting differences in opinion, background, and experience. We do not tolerate discrimination or harassment of any kind.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-600 font-medium italic">
            <li>Verbal or physical abuse</li>
            <li>Sexual harassment or unwanted attention</li>
            <li>Cyberbullying or online harassment</li>
            <li>Discrimination based on race, ethnicity, gender, sexual orientation, religion, or disability</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Inclusivity & Responsibility</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">
            We welcome all individuals regardless of their background. We are committed to creating a space where everyone feels comfortable. All individuals are responsible for their own actions and must behave in a safe, professional manner during all community activities.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 bg-blue-50 rounded-[2rem] border border-blue-100">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4 italic">Neutrality & Fairness</h2>
          <p class="text-blue-800 font-medium">
            Stay Neutral and Fair to all. To ensure a fair and non-partisan environment, all members, especially executives and captains, must refrain from political engagement or union activities within the community context.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Institutional Compliance</h2>
          <p>
            Every participant must follow the rules and guidelines of <span class="font-bold">Nepal College of Information Technology (NCIT)</span>, as well as the community's own constitution and policies.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="p-8 bg-orange-50 rounded-[2rem] border border-orange-100">
             <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-orange-900 mb-4">Reporting Violations</h2>
             <p class="text-orange-800 text-sm italic">
               If you see or experience any behavior that violates this code, please report it to a member of the NTK leadership team immediately.
             </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 bg-red-50 rounded-[2rem] border border-red-100">
             <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-red-900 mb-4">Enforcement</h2>
             <p class="text-red-800 text-sm">
               The NTK executive team reserves the right to remove any individual from community activities or membership if they violate these standards.
             </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-20 pt-10 border-t border-gray-100 text-center text-gray-400 font-medium">
        Nepal Tek Community â€” Empowering through technology, anchored in respect.
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
